NowTalk Wordpress Plugin

This plugin allows you to easily add the NowTalk chat widget to your Wordpress blog

To Install:

1.  Install the plugin from the plugin directory
2.  Go to Settings->NowTalk
3.  At the minimum set the Site ID that you were given
4.  After submitting your changes, NowTalk should show up on your blog

Contact us at: info@nowtalk.com for questions or problems